<reference id="class_rtcsurfaceview">
    <title><ph keyref="RtcSurfaceView"/></title>
    <shortdesc id="short"><ph id="shortdesc">The RtcSurfaceView class.</ph></shortdesc>
    <refbody>
        <section id="detailed_desc">
            <p>This class is used to render:</p>
            <ul>
            <li>Android: This class corresponds to the native SurfaceView.</li>
            <li>iOS: This class corresponds to the native UIView.</li>
            </ul> 
            <p>为保证渲染出图，调用该组件前，根据当前是否加入频道进行对应操作：</p>
            <ul>               
                <li>Not joining a channel: Call  <xref keyref="startPreview2"/>first<xref keyref="enableVideo"/>.</li>
                <li>加入频道时：先开启采集，。 然后调用<xref keyref="enableVideo"/></li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </refbody>
</reference>
